Cyberpunk style: A sprawling neon-lit cityscape at night where towering buildings are interconnected by glowing data streams and fiber optic cables forming an intricate web. In the foreground, a massive transparent cube floats mid-air, containing smaller modular geometric shapes that click together like puzzle pieces, each glowing with different electric colors - cyan, magenta, and gold. The shapes cast holographic reflections onto rain-slicked streets below. Steam rises from vents, mixing with the ambient glow. The architecture features sharp angular designs with circuit-board patterns etched into building facades. Small drones zip between the structures carrying packets of light. The scene conveys the concept of modular services connecting and working together within a larger system, emphasizing clean separation yet seamless integration.
